  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the progression of ET in children (aged 6-17years
      inclusive) over a period of 5 years maximum. The study will also assess how children are
      diagnosed, treatment options for those children with symptoms and events related to their ET
      and the outcomes of those treatments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
